        </div>

        <img src="~/Content/images/infosvg/good.svg" class="col-span-1">
        <p class="col-span-3 text-btn">
            Using more durale fabrics which mean customers can wear them longer
        </p>
        <img src="~/Content/images/infosvg/goodqual.svg" class="col-span-1">

        <img src="~/Content/images/infosvg/waste.svg" class="col-span-1">
        <p class="col-span-3 text-bad">
            Manufacturing practices which result in a large amount of textile waste
        </p>
        <img src="~/Content/images/infosvg/bad.svg" class="col-span-1">

        <div class="col-start-6 col-span-2">
            <h5 class="mb-2 text-2xl font-bold text-center tracking-tight text-CardText">Waste</h5>
        </div>

        <img src="~/Content/images/infosvg/good.svg" class="col-span-1">
        <p class="col-span-3 text-btn">
            Being considerate of resources and finding optimal uses for leftover textiles
        </p>
        <img src="~/Content/images/infosvg/recycle.svg" class="col-span-1">

