            <h5 class="mb-2 text-2xl font-bold text-center tracking-tight text-CardText">Pollution</h5>
        </div>

        <img src="~/Content/images/infosvg/good.svg" class="col-span-1">
        <p class="col-span-3 text-btn">
            Eco friendly materials and production practices such as using renewable energy sources
        </p>
        <img src="~/Content/images/infosvg/ecofri.svg" class="col-span-1">

