            <h5 class="mb-2 text-2xl font-bold text-center tracking-tight text-CardText">Manufacturing Location</h5>
        </div>

        <img src="~/Content/images/infosvg/good.svg" class="col-span-1">
        <p class="col-span-3 text-btn">
            Manufacturing in locally to reduce transport and packaging
        </p>
        <img src="~/Content/images/infosvg/reducepack.svg" class="col-span-1">

