            </div>

        </div>
        <div class="col-span-3 bg-bggrey items-center justify-center">

            <ul class="space-y-10 mr-10 my-10 bg-bggrey items-center justify-center text-center">
                <li class="flex items-center">
                    <img src="~/Content/images/infosvg/1.svg" class="mx-10 justify-center">
                    <span>Use our <a href="#" class="underline text-btn">fashion footprint calculator</a> to work out what impact your fashion consumption behaviours are having on the planet</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center">
                    <img src="~/Content/images/infosvg/2.svg" class="mx-10 justify-center">
                    <span>Choose clothing made from <a href="#" class="underline text-btn">sustainable fabrics</a> such as organic cotton and recycled fibres</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center">
                    <img src="~/Content/images/infosvg/3.svg" class="mx-10 justify-center">
                    <span>When buying from <a href="#" class="underline text-btn">sustainable brands</a> you send a message that ethical practices are important</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center">
                    <img src="~/Content/images/infosvg/4.svg" class="mx-10 justify-center">
                    <span>Throw out your old clothes by donating to <a href="#" class="underline text-btn">recycling organizations</a> . who can give it another life</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center">
                    <img src="~/Content/images/infosvg/5.svg" class="mx-10 justify-center">
                    <span>
                        Before buying something new, look through your wardrobe and consider whether it is really necessary
                    </span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center">
                    <img src="~/Content/images/infosvg/6.svg" class="mx-10 justify-center">
                    <span>
                        Explore op shops and second hand marketplaces to give someone elses clothes another life
                    </span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center">
                    <img src="~/Content/images/infosvg/7.svg" class="mx-10 justify-center">
                    <span>
                        Invest in timeless, high quality clothing to reduce the frequency of your purchases
                    </span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center">
                    <img src="~/Content/images/infosvg/8.svg" class="mx-10 justify-center">
                    <span>
                        Take care of your clothes by following care instructions and repairing when needed
                    </span>
                </li>
            </ul>

        </div>
    </div>
    <script>
        document.querySelectorAll('a.slidebutton').forEach(anchor => {
            anchor.addEventListener('click', function (e) {
                e.preventDefault();
                const targetId = this.getAttribute('href').substring(1);
                const targetElement = document.getElementById(targetId);
                if (targetElement) {
                    const targetPosition = targetElement.offsetTop - 70;
                    window.scrollTo({ top: targetPosition, behavior: 'smooth' });
                }
            });
        });
    </script>

</div>
